{"tid":2379034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍社區關注組 小朋友俾廢老打","createTime":"2021-01-25T03:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T15:58:17.000Z","uid":64603,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"afa74a7f4626973fadd9781de035956495b9df4b","tid":2379034,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:16:54.000Z","msg":"「天水圍社區關注組」創辦人兼主席、現年只有11歲的小六生王繼祖（Joel），據悉周日（24日）於天秀路公園巡區期間，發現一群「大媽」及老翁聚集跳舞，他提醒對方收細音量時，疑遭一名老翁頭撼門牙及毆打腹部。<br />\n<br />\n由事發片段可見，兩人爭執期間，涉事老翁撞向王繼祖。王繼祖慨嘆：「依家連做社區工作都會被人打！」他晚上前往警署報案，並到醫院驗傷。警方回覆查詢時表示，經初步調查後，案件列作「普通襲擊」處理。<br />\n<br />\nhk01 唔貼link<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">天水圍社區關注組係咩嚟？</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3tP10U7anps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3tP10U7anps&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=d3dbef1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3tP10U7anps</a>"},{"pid":"3ce3ed3be49626cdc405cf8d586b4e176959d2da","tid":2379034,"uid":281492,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:17:32.000Z","msg":"細路都蝦，祝個阿伯過唔到年"},{"pid":"4cea77b4f34ecd5f8144be96fdc8d3e5fe01f87b","tid":2379034,"uid":210731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48400989ccd28e408268f530acc0eb644bb6e950","tid":2379034,"uid":184261,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:19:53.000Z","msg":"民智仍然未開"},{"pid":"99f69fd777d310c2b9604064db30feeb0280f891","tid":2379034,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"死廢老"},{"pid":"5efde99d740c446bb0d5190a4b0ca0cf2df784dd","tid":2379034,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"48400989ccd28e408268f530acc0eb644bb6e950","tid":2379034,"uid":184261,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:19:53.000Z","msg":"民智仍然未開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:24:27.000Z","msg":"你好醒？"